description: The Buffalo Truck is bringing Buffalo Style to southern California. What is Buffalo Style? Buffalo Style is where the food is covered in a vinegar style hot sauce (Franks Red Hot) and is accompanied with blue cheese or Ranch in some form of dressing or sauce. We bring our Buffalo Style flavor to our wings, chicken fingers, mac-n-cheese, sandwiches, soups, quesadillas, wraps, salads, and shrimp.
name: The Buffalo Truck
